<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mhmạ smt ậmạlnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mhmạ smt ậmạlnạ .. ạ̉w ʿẓmt ạ̉hdạfnạ
 mḥqquⁿ wṣwlnạ .. mw̉kduⁿ njạḥnạ
 ạlqrạr- (lạ̉nnạ qạdrwn .. yswʿ gẖạlb ạlmnwn
 fy ạlqlb yḥyạ ky nkwn .. dwmaⁿạ bh qạdryn)2
 2- mhmạ gẖdt ạ̉ḥwạlnạ .. ạ̉w hạj fynạ bḥrnạ
 lạ kẖwf fy qlwbnạ .. bl dạỷmuⁿ slạmnạ
 3- mhmạ dnạ ʿdwnạ .. mḥạwlạaⁿ tfsẖylnạ
 mtẖbt ạ̹ymạnnạ .. whkdẖạ ạntṣạrnạ
 4- ṭwạl ʿmrnạ hnạ .. kdẖạk fy smạỷnạ
 ln ynthy tsbyḥnạ .. wạlsẖkr mn qlwbnạ</lyrics>
<hymn_number>806</hymn_number>
<author>shyl mdạnạt, jmạl ḥsẖwẗ</author>
</song>